                      <name>.lzx.js -> compileInBrowser(sprites:none, proxied:false,
                      cache) + ETag/304; app-rel lps/* runtime resources -> proxied to
                      LPS_URL; else pass-through. skipWaiting()/clients.claim().
                      Config: LPS_URL, RUNTIME_URL, APPS registry (virtual .lzx URLs
                      under SW scope so plain python http.server works, no
